Conclusions
{AKT}1 E17K is a bona fide oncogene in a human luminal breast cancer context. Distinct {PI}3K pathway mutations confer differential sensitivity to drugs targeting the pathway at different points and by distinct mechanisms. These findings have implications for the use of tumor genome sequencing to assign patients to targeted therapies.},
